flowchart TD
  alert[Alert Received] --> triage[Triage Incident]
  triage --> severity[Severity Decision]
  severity -->|High| commander[Assign Incident Commander]
  severity -->|Medium| patch[Deploy Patch]
  severity -->|Low| backlog[Schedule Fix]
  commander --> comms[Send Status Update]
  patch --> comms
  backlog --> comms
  comms --> close[Close Incident]
